B3 addresses critical pain points in onchain gaming:Fragmentation: By connecting multiple chains, B3 eliminates the need for players to navigate disjointed networks.
User Experience: Its chain abstraction and instant login features make gaming accessible to non-crypto users.
Scalability: Horizontally scaled appchains provide dedicated blockspace for high-performance gaming.
Developer Support: Comprehensive tools and white-glove support enable developers to build and scale quickly.

Unlike other gaming chains that prioritize vanity metrics, B3 focuses on “fun-first” experiences, restoring economic freedom for creators and players through decentralized ownership and interoperable assets.

